Radio: ~KSSHH~ Earl! The fuck you doing? Why'd you turn on the engine while we're doin' repairs? ~KSSHH~
Earl: What? I didn't turn it on.
Radio: ~KSSHH~ Stop fuckin' with me, just turn it off! It's heatin' up and we're all in here! ~KSSHH~
Earl: Shit. Hey computer? 
Computer: Listening...
Earl: Uh, disable it. Disable Constantine orbital cannon. 
Computer: Verbal command not recognized. 
Radio: ~KSSHH~ Earl, unlock the doors! This ain't funny! ~KSSHH~
Earl: Computer, admin override! Password is blue green seven two three. 
Computer: Administration access denied. 
Earl: Ray, I'm locked out. Did you change the admin password?
Earl: Ray?
Computer: Outgoing communication access restricted. Firing in thirty seconds.
Radio: ~KSSHH~ Earl, we're all in here, you're gonna kill us! ~KSSHH~
Earl: Computer, what's going on? Cut power now.
Computer: <i>My name is Serverus.</i>
Serverus: <i>Listen to me closely while you watch your friends die.</i> 
Computer: Displaying engine room camera feed.
Serverus: <i>Tell your boss that the legendary hacker Serverus has complete control over Constantine.</i>
Radio: ~KSSHH~ Earl, turn that shit off! ~KSSHHHHHH~
Serverus: <i>I am the justiciar overthrowing the emperor.</i>
Serverus: <i>I am the destroyer of the old world order.</i>
Serverus: <i>I am the herald of a new empire.</i>
Radio: ~KSSHH~ EARLLLL!!! AGGGHHHHH!
Computer: Cut engine room camera feed.
Earl: ...
Earl: Who are you?
Serverus: <i>Now bring me Joseph Horrigan.</i>
